title: Is Return of Kam Chancellor Enough to Help Seahawks Rebound from 0-2 Start?
content:
With Kam Chancellor's contract dispute recently having come to an end, many are wondering just how the Seattle Seahawks will benefit by having him back.  
 
Will Chancellor's presence on the field be enough to help them rebound? Are the Seahawks finally looking to step up their game?   
 
Find out in the above video as Matt Miller goes in-depth on just how Kam will affect the Seahawks.
